e_104mvf1665703198985.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mvf1665703198985.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mvf1665703198985.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mvf1665703198985\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Remove all state information from USTATE, prior to a specified date.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__topic_d135803e1_d135804e1_d135805e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__p_d135806e1_d135807e1_d135808e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">\"USYSSTAT\".CleanUpState</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">TimeStamp</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__section_N10034_N10016_N10001\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__4\">Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">TimeStamp</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mvf1665703198985__table_d16259e1_d16260e1_d16261e1__entry__4\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DateTime</span> value. If 0 or and\n                        empty string (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>), all occurrences will be removed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__section_n1p_gdg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d697367e132\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__p_d135812e1_d135813e1_d135814e1\">Use this operation for bulk cleanup actions on the\n            USTATE table</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__p_d135815e1_d135816e1_d135817e1\">The following operation deletes all state records\n            that are more than 24 hours old.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mvf1665703198985_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mvf1665703198985__codeblock_xdv_jdg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation cleanState\nvariables\n datetime vDate\nendvariables\nvDate = $datim - 24h ; current date and time minus 24 hours\nactivate \"USYSSTAT\".CleanUpState(vDate)\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bot