eration deletes all state records that are more than 24 hours old. Explain this code operation cleanState variables datetime vDate endvariables vDate = $datim - 24h ; current date and time minus 24 hours activate \"USYSSTAT\".CleanUpState(vDate) end Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}